OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,FCampaigners are celebrating after
OL,7,FBristol City Council announced a major
OL,8,F#18million refurbishment of its
OL,9,Fhousing in St Jude's that has been
OL,10,Fdelayed for over a decade.
OL,12,FThe funding will be spent upgrading
OL,13,Ffive blocks ` John Cozens House,
OL,14,FHaviland House, Charleton House,
OL,15,FLangton House and Tyndall House ` with
OL,16,Fa total of 180 flats, of which 163 are
OL,17,Foccupied.
