OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,FFourteen families will be asked to
OL,7,Fmove out for up to three months while
OL,8,Fengineers carry out survey work, and
OL,9,Fthey will be found other council
OL,10,Faccommodation or can stay with friends
OL,11,For family and receive some financial
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,FRepairs will include new roofs,
OL,15,Ffloors, doors, windows, lighting,
OL,16,Fexternal wall insulation, enclosed
OL,17,Fstaircases, electrical works, smoke
OL,18,Fdetectors, bike racks and bin stores.
