OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,FCity Hall housing chiefs say there are
OL,7,Fno structural concerns despite the
OL,8,Ffact the tower blocks have a similar
OL,9,Fdesign to Barton House, where the
OL,10,Flocal authority declared a 'major
OL,11,Fincident' in November amid fears the
OL,12,Fbuilding could collapse if there was a
OL,13,Ffire in a single flat.
OL,15,FAbout 400 tenants and leaseholders
OL,16,Fwere evacuated, mostly into hotels,
OL,17,Fbut further surveys showed the Barton
OL,18,FHill high-rise was fundamentally safe
OL,19,Fand they were allowed to return home
OL,20,Ffour months later.
