OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,FThe refurbishment programme in St
OL,7,FJude's, near Cabot Circus, will be
OL,8,Fdone in phases and take three to five
OL,9,Fyears to complete.
OL,11,FIt signals victory for residents who
OL,12,Flaunched a campaign backed by
OL,13,Fcommunity union ACORN over the
OL,14,Fdreadful state of their council flats.
OL,16,FSt Jude's resident and ACORN member
OL,17,FYasmin said: "I can't describe what a
OL,18,Fmonumental win these new developments
OL,19,Fwill be for our community.
