OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,F"After many years fading into the
OL,7,Fbackground, our homes neglected and
OL,8,Fforgotten, with the much appreciated
OL,9,Fhelp and dedication from ACORN we
OL,10,Fbanded together as residents and
OL,11,Ffought for our voices to be heard.
OL,13,F"At the end of the day, these flats
OL,14,Fare home to many complex and intricate
OL,15,Findividual lives, where we raise our
OL,16,Fchildren and lay to rest at night.
OL,18,F"We are not just statistics on a sheet
OL,19,Fof paper or boxes to be ticked.
