OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,F"It's brilliant to feel such hope for
OL,7,Fmyself and my fellow residents of St
OL,8,FJude's for the first time in my seven
OL,9,Fyears living here."
OL,11,FAnother neighbour and ACORN member
OL,12,FMohamed said: "The council ignored us
OL,13,Ffor years, but after we marched on the
OL,14,Fcouncil building together they started
OL,15,Fto listen.
OL,17,F"Last month we took action again,
OL,18,Fpushing council leaders for when they
OL,19,Fwould start working to make our homes
OL,20,Fsafe, and now we see concrete plans `
OL,21,Fit's brilliant."
