OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,FThe announcement on 13 June came as
OL,7,Fthe authority delivered leaflets to
OL,8,Feveryone in the blocks explaining what
OL,9,Fwould happen.
OL,11,FIn a press briefing on Thursday
OL,12,Fafternoon, a council spokesperson said
OL,13,Fofficers and contractors would work
OL,14,Fwith the community on the final
OL,15,Fdesigns and that building work itself
OL,16,Fwas expected to start around the end
OL,17,Fof the year after the results of the
OL,18,Fsurveys were known, but that initial
OL,19,Ffindings had shown no concerns.
