OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,FThey said: "These blocks have been
OL,7,Foverdue a refurbishment for a very
OL,8,Flong time.
OL,10,F"They have been unfortunately subject
OL,11,Fto water ingress and have a lot of
OL,12,Fwear and tear. It's a campaign the
OL,13,Fresidents have taken to City Hall.
OL,15,F"We are now in a place where we can
OL,16,Fstart that refurbishment. There has
OL,17,Fbeen an ambition to do this for over a
OL,18,Fdecade. We apologise that it has taken
OL,19,Fso long.
