OL,3,CFive tower blocks to be refurbished in
OL,4,C'overdue' council housing upgrade
OL,6,F"A lot of this work will be focused on
OL,7,Fimproving the energy efficiency of the
OL,8,Fblocks."
OL,10,FThe spokesperson said the delays had
OL,11,Fbeen a combination of finances, the
OL,12,Fpandemic, requirements to improve fire
OL,13,Fsafety and cladding in blocks
OL,14,Ffollowing the Grenfell disaster and,
OL,15,Fmostly recently, resources having to
OL,16,Fbe redirected to sort the issues at
OL,17,FBarton House.
